---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — Top Gear Decide"
  description="Top Gear Decide is reader-supported and uses affiliate links, including the Amazon Associates Program. Here's exactly what that means for you."
  path="/affiliate-disclosure"
>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="container page-wrap">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="lead">Last updated: 2025</p>

      <p>Top Gear Decide (topgeardecide.com) is reader-supported. To keep our reviews free and our research independent, we use affiliate links throughout the site. This page explains exactly what that means for you.</p>

      <h2>Amazon Associates Program</h2>
      <p>Top Gear Decide is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com. When you click an Amazon link on our site and make a qualifying purchase, we may receive a small commission.</p>

      <h2>What This Costs You</h2>
      <p>Nothing. Affiliate commissions are paid by the retailer, not by you. You pay the same price whether you reach a product through one of our links or by visiting the store directly. The commission simply helps fund the time we spend researching and maintaining our guides.</p>

      <h2>Other Affiliate Partners</h2>
      <p>In addition to Amazon, we may participate in other affiliate and advertising programs with retailers and brands relevant to food, supplements and drinks. In every case, the same standards apply: links are added for products we believe are worth your consideration.</p>

      <h2>How It Affects Our Reviews</h2>
      <p>It doesn't change our verdicts. We rank and recommend products based on their merits — ingredient quality, nutrition, value and suitability for different goals and diets. A product does not earn a higher position because it pays a larger commission, and we regularly recommend options that earn us little or nothing when they are genuinely the best choice. If we ever cannot recommend a product, we will not feature it just to place a link.</p>

      <h2>Pricing and Availability</h2>
      <p>Prices, availability and product formulations change frequently. Any figures mentioned on our site are accurate to the best of our knowledge at the time of writing but should be confirmed on the retailer's page before you buy.</p>

      <h2>Not Medical Advice</h2>
      <p>Our reviews of supplements and dietary products are for general information only and are not medical or nutritional advice. Always read the product label and consult a qualified healthcare professional before adding a new supplement or dietary product to your routine.</p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>If anything here is unclear, please reach out through our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page. We're happy to explain how we operate.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us by Email</h2>
      <p>You can also reach us directly by email:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>General questions &amp; feedback: <a href="mailto:info@topgeardecide.com">info@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
        <li>Advertising &amp; affiliate partnerships: <a href="mailto:affiliate@topgeardecide.com">affiliate@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
